{"tid":2156293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d 軍裝差佬係咪唔使再戴帽？？","createTime":"2020-08-14T10:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:14:46.000Z","uid":1654,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"84adf6b9acf23a0b86a40bfe79f8e5270f93988a","tid":2156293,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCMATPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCMATPy.jpg&h=6e82e82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMRk4WM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMRk4WM.png&h=270a6c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E915wBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE915wBM.jpg&h=909035ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PhB1Pos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhB1Pos.jpg&h=0be8958b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來之前有差佬提過話唔撚戴，<br />\n但係警司（策劃行動）支援科 羅卓洪就咁講：<br />\n軍裝警務人員當值時是必須穿制服的。警帽是警察制服的一部分，而警察制服的作用在於使市民容易辨認警察的身份。警帽亦為多年來建立下來的警察形象的一個不可分割部分。<br />\n<br />\n世界各地的警務人員均佩戴警帽。<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">警帽象徵正義</span></span>，一般警務人員均以戴上警帽為傲。對信中提及警帽予人敵意或威嚇的感覺，請恕本人不能同意。事實上，警帽亦為佩戴者帶來多方面保護。<br />\n<br />\n警隊一向致力改善裝備及制服，現時正就警帽進行檢討，希望引入較現時為舒適及透氣的警帽以供警務人員佩戴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/665/072_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F665%2F072_c.htm&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=fcb3daac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/665/072_c.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5bEA3B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5bEA3B.png&h=d522c404&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QH8cbBX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQH8cbBX.png&h=0d0f7397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n原來警帽象徵正義，唔怪得唔撚戴/唔敢戴"},{"pid":"dbebadb00c548e789de6e535fa9109e3283d2244","tid":2156293,"uid":96767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"我建議戴 狗帶 狗罩。聽到班垃圾吠就想毒啞佢哋"},{"pid":"e4b9e6ca018ce6199af08e1ca640fe458baf0ef9","tid":2156293,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"373bec47900cc77572a966aa59febf4218303662","tid":2156293,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"遲啲可能連衫都唔使攝"},{"pid":"484e721a3e8ae7ac99f062d1cc3a999786372dd0","tid":2156293,"uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Omtuq2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Omtuq2.gif&h=41b2da0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小心俾人有機可乘"},{"pid":"573644eadd71f6cbc7e81e93b63bbbdd1a849ac6","tid":2156293,"uid":81336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"建議換晒做背心短褲 咁就方便晒捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b8a7be24ef0d1ba337675d713bc848e52e7e8f","tid":2156293,"uid":3249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"証都冇 是撚旦啦"},{"pid":"650a2a4af9be5a668dae080f57f29931c236db3d","tid":2156293,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/03/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD-%E8%80%81%E5%B1%88%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-20180301225900_e0f3_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD-%25E8%2580%25